### Pattern 3: Using DMMFHelper for Advanced Operations

**From:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775389478214-8x8i0j/packages/client-generator-ts/src/dmmf.ts`

